WEB DEVELOPMENT: VIDEO GAME INFORMATION PLATFORM BY ANGULAR

● Developed a comprehensive video game information platform using Angular CLI, integrating real-time data from a public API (Rapid API).

● Utilized TypeScript and SCSS to build robust and maintainable code, adhering to best practices for Angular development.

● Designed and implemented multiple Angular components, including a search and filter bar, game details view, home page, and game tab, to provide a user-friendly interface for exploring and interacting with video game data.

● Leveraged Angular services for efficient HTTP calls to retrieve and display game information, enhancing the platform's responsiveness and performance.

● Implemented HTTP interceptors to enhance data security and streamline API requests.

● Established application routing to ensure smooth navigation and user experience.
